</caption>
<paragraph id="8BB736AC2028FF8FFB00CA31F9E629B6" blockId="0.[1256,2135,1085,1272]" pageId="0" pageNumber="186">• Mainly near shore and continental shelf, but also continental slope areas.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB736AC2028FF8FFB00CAE5F9EC29CE" blockId="0.[1256,2135,1085,1272]" box="[1256,1583,1204,1233]" pageId="0" pageNumber="186">• 2 genera, 4 species.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB736AC2028FF8FFB00CA86F82229E7" blockId="0.[1256,2135,1085,1272]" box="[1256,2017,1239,1272]" pageId="0" pageNumber="186">• 2 species Endangered; none Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
